{"tid":1209014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"行緊去就海富中心 忍唔住喊咗出黎","createTime":"2019-06-12T10:42:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T11:18:51.000Z","uid":91884,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"06b37d86b1a03556b33c76dc38bdd80fe38dd2e3","tid":1209014,"uid":91884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T10:42:17.000Z","msg":"我後到 唯有自己過去<br />\n啲人一路逆方向散緊 同時間就爆左一幾粒<br />\n我又已經行左半路 諗住行埋<br />\n同學仔好細心 經過每個都問我要唔要生理鹽水<br />\n<br />\n最撚心痛係見到有啲人頭也不回就走左<br />\n有人仲嗌緊<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好走呀翻黎呀</span><br />\n啲煙雖然係好攻眼 但果刻唔知點解好驚 好心痛<br />\n香港人如果再就咁行咗去 唔知仲有冇機會可以表達意見<br />\n喊到仆街所以隻眼好快就冇事<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人加油</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LzBrQJz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLzBrQJz.png&h=9928eb52&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nnvcMgU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnnvcMgU.png&h=d7b1f973&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"86708cd4286e52509866a2fe2d93786c742f6279","tid":1209014,"uid":91884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T11:18:51.000Z","msg":"但係奉勸一句 我地去嘅目的唔係屌佢地老母<br />\n甚至唔係林奠下台<br />\n而係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">撤回！</span>"}]}